{"tid":923418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台鐵疑現癡漢列車　多名妙齡女遭下體磨蹭 獵物都是約18歲","createTime":"2018-12-01T08:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T10:36:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"adf0bf1df5a7b25d8d739679009ddc265ca06ebb","tid":923418,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"台鐵出現電車之狼！網友在《爆料公社》PO文，指稱今天下午有一名身穿黑衣、戴黑框眼鏡的年輕男子，搭乘桃園到台北的區間車，趁著人潮擁擠時，用下體磨蹭身旁的年輕女性，旁邊的乘客見狀後錄影並提醒被害人，後來男子在萬華站下車，幾名受害女性則一起到鐵警報案。<br />\n<br />\nPO文的廖姓網友指稱，這名男子之前就被人盯上，這回又跑到電車伸狼爪，被發現後還若無其事地換位置尋找獵物，旁人都看不下去，不斷提醒被害人趕快離開，男子知道東窗事發，趕緊在萬華站下車，五名受害人目前已到鐵警局台北分駐所報案。網友說，「真的有夠可惡，一趟車就騷擾好幾位！」並希望其他證人出面到警局指認。<br />\n台北分駐所所長蘇中泰表示，稍早有民眾帶著幾名18歲上下的年輕女子來報案，熱心民眾說，「他們被性騷擾。」幾名年輕女子說，「有覺得電車上很擠，沒有發現被性騷擾。」是旁人提醒才覺得「怪怪的」，但都不願意提告。警方已派員到萬華站調閱相關監視影像，仍在釐清這名男子身分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181201/1476562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476562&d=6QdQly7TZhMNNtULIaCvDqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=0dd416bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181201%2F1476562&h=e7dadb25\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181201/1476562</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_11235aa95e864a968f6006dc6e17a937.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_11235aa95e864a968f6006dc6e17a937.jpg&h=09a3eb82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_50da3dcb7bcab1c4d69fed1914660ca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_50da3dcb7bcab1c4d69fed1914660ca0.jpg&h=908a4a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_3ccf921ccc1e9158433356fff5257bd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_3ccf921ccc1e9158433356fff5257bd8.jpg&h=2e0120d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181201/640_a94ed5b4015640264757ebd19a6b48cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181201%2F640_a94ed5b4015640264757ebd19a6b48cc.jpg&h=b8d90323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一張不錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf10f0456947179f27f73d51d0841430dd20099","tid":923418,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0081a2e5b6557e48d768d8f8ec564d8111f39101","tid":923418,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf10f0456947179f27f73d51d0841430dd20099","tid":923418,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔磨爆好彩"}]}